item.title: The mod tahorks ultamite server guide help
item.dc:creator: @soadfreek409 soadfreek409
item.description:
@soadfreek409 wrote:

No, you go to your router… http://(yourIP), Then everyones router is different so, I go to Applications and Gaming then it brings up a whole list of port forwarding lines… simply enter your desired port and enter the last 3 number of your IP (which is found by double clicking the connection icon at bottom of screen). Save changes then you can play… after you run the server of course…
